      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and honestly drives like a dream! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and while it\u2019s seen some fun adventures, it\u2019s still got so much life left to give. It\u2019s the perfect balance of quality and value\u2014super dependable and ready to hit the road today. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come by, say hi, and take it for a spin!",
