    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical maintenance is up to date, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement for long-term reliability. The chassis remains rigid with a reinforced rear subframe, while the suspension utilizes Bilstein B16 coilovers for enhanced lateral grip and dampening control. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its factory paint with minor patina consistent with age, and the interior features Nappa leather with minimal bolster wear. A precision-engineered driver\u2019s car for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Well-maintained engine and interior. Reliable daily driver. Ready for immediate sale.",
